	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64466441"><p><div class="quote"><p>Who'll go to jail?</p></div><p>Nobody.</p><p>If you want to put people in jail for stupidity and incompetence, you'll need to build a lot more jails.</p><p>The decisions that killed people were the lack of redundant sensors on the 737MAX and skimping on pilot training, both of which were approved by the FAA.</p></div>
